<img src="{{ email.image('@images/ishtar-logo.png') }}" alt="Logo">

<h1>Hello {{ artistName }}!</h1>

<h2>This is your weekly report from Ishtar:</h2>

<p>
    <i> You have {{ artistFollowers }} followers.</i>
</p>

<h3>Here is your paintings report:</h3>

    {% for detail in details %}
        <h4><strong>Painting name: {{ detail.name }}</h4>
        <li>views: {{ detail.viewed }}</li>
        <li>followers: {{ detail.follower }}</li>
        <li>likes: {{ detail.likes }}</li>
        <li>comments: {{ detail.comments }}</li>
        <li>claps: {{ detail.claps }}</li>
        <br>
    {% endfor %}

<p>Please tell us if there are any updates you would like to do with your painting like sale or information update.</p>
<p>Thank you</p>
<p>
    <a href="http://www.ishtar-art.de">ISHTAR</a> team.
</p>